3160.Name: 2021 Chatham Paddle Mixed Doubles Tournament
3160.Details: INVITE ONLY Each partnership must be comprised of one male and one female player. All pairs will enter double-elimination bracketed play, with winners of each bracket meeting for the grand finals.
3160.RegistrationDetails: IMPORTANT INSTRUCTIONS: To register, please type your name in the search box where it says "If you are a current player, enter your name to register." If your name does not come up, try it just using your last name. DO NOT click on the link that says "If you are new to the league, click here to fill out the form." If you have any trouble finding your name, please contact us but just do not create a new account. Once you proceed to the second page after finding your name, fill out the form.
